com.google.gwt.dev.shell
Class CompilingClassLoader

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.ClassLoader
      com.google.gwt.dev.shell.CompilingClassLoader
All Implemented Interfaces:
DispatchIdOracle
public final class CompilingClassLoader
extends java.lang.ClassLoader
implements DispatchIdOracle

An isolated ClassLoader for running all user code. All user files are compiled from source code byte a ByteCodeCompiler. After compilation, some byte code rewriting is performed to support JavaScriptObject and its subtypes. TODO: we should refactor this class to move the getClassInfoByDispId, getDispId, getMethodDispatch and putMethodDispatch into a separate entity since they really do not interact with the CompilingClassLoader functionality.
